@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - Check-out, Overstay và Override
autonumber
skinparam maxMessageSize 160
skinparam sequence {
    ParticipantPadding 20
    MessageAlign center
}

actor "Bộ lập lịch" as Scheduler
actor "Lễ tân" as Receptionist
boundary "POS" as POS
control "Operation Service" as OperationService
control "Waitlist Service" as WaitlistService
database "Database" as DB

== 1. Giám sát overstay ==
Scheduler -> OperationService : monitorOverstay(now)
OperationService -> DB : Tìm Reservation.status = SEATED\nvà now > end_time

loop Với mỗi reservation bị overstay
    OperationService -> DB : Update Table_Info.status = OVERSTAY
    OperationService --> POS : Push cảnh báo vận hành
end

== 2. Check-out bình thường ==
Receptionist -> POS : Check-out(reservation_id)
POS -> OperationService : checkOut(reservationId, now)
OperationService -> DB : Update Reservation.status = COMPLETED
OperationService -> DB : Update Reservation.end_time = now
OperationService -> Scheduler : releaseTablesAfterBuffer(reservationId)

Scheduler -> DB : Sau buffer time, update Table_Info.status = AVAILABLE
Scheduler -> WaitlistService : notifyNextCandidate()
WaitlistService -> DB : Lấy khách WAITING phù hợp theo joined_at
WaitlistService --> POS : Gợi ý Notify Waitlist / Seat Waitlist

== 3. Xử lý xung đột overstay ==
note over Receptionist, POS
  Trường hợp walk-in overstay gây xung đột với booking online,
  lễ tân phải yêu cầu khách rời bàn trước.
  Chỉ trong tình huống bất khả kháng mới được override.
end note

Receptionist -> POS : Yêu cầu khách overstay rời bàn

alt Khách chấp hành
    POS -> OperationService : checkOut(reservationId, now)
    OperationService -> DB : Update Reservation.status = COMPLETED
    OperationService -> DB : Update Reservation.end_time = now
    OperationService -> Scheduler : releaseTablesAfterBuffer(reservationId)

else Tình huống bất khả kháng
    Receptionist -> POS : Override(reservation_id, reason)
    POS -> OperationService : overrideConflict(reservationId, accountId, reason)
    OperationService -> DB : Insert Override_Log(reservation_id, account_id, reason, created_at)
    OperationService -> DB : Cập nhật Reservation/Table_Info theo phương án xử lý thủ công
    OperationService --> POS : Override đã được ghi nhận
end

@enduml
